<a href=\"https://lihkg.com/thread/405047/page/1?ref=web\" target=\"_blank\">https://lihkg.com/thread/405047/page/1?ref=web</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區"},{"pid":"51401ace23d969614cde6f1867b06031ee695d71","tid":404747,"uid":44358,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-18T14:12:44.000Z","msg":"巴塞唔夠皇馬踢，所以加泰羅尼亞要求獨立<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4771e203606c0c6ddcc8da8c4f148ab02fbb11b5","tid":404747,"uid":90606,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-18T14:20:40.000Z","msg":"條友真係痴撚左線<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n講到香港學生咁廢 咁你d支那狗仲落黎"},{"pid":"f9490a7ca39457b330bf21c580f92daabc67fb21","tid":404747,"uid":11001,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-18T14:35:18.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>條友真係痴撚左線<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n講到香港學生咁廢 咁你d支那狗仲落黎</blockquote><br />\n【本報訊】（記者　伍敏婷）本月11日將是中學會考放榜的日子，數萬名莘莘學子都在焦急地等待這一天。教統局局長李國章表示，會考成績並非決定人生成敗的主要因素，只要考生繼續努力，必會有美好的出路。「香港並沒有失敗的學生，若果有，也是教育制度的責任。」<br />\n<br />\n若果香港學生係loser嘅話，李國章本人責無旁貸 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f43ccb2aeab1902c059796303050e1dbae04e99a","tid":404747,"uid":65074,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-18T14:42:43.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 李國章發表出位言論博上位<br />\n<br />\n(套用班老屎忽邏輯)"},{"pid":"310674819fc738884ceadbcb829a05abc5c4e0c8","tid":404747,"uid":35430,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-18T14:47:12.000Z","msg":"咁獨左競爭力高左咪夠實力同大陸砌囉<br />\n長遠對香港係好事"},{"pid":"7adc4df82ebb06bce291bf24221d493cac18ead5","tid":404747,"uid":45170,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-18T15:11:35.000Z","msg":"岩先睇到<img src=\"/assets/faces/n